Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:12.72,Main,,0,0,0,,It was the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:13.89,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:18.06,Main,,0,0,0,,...I was able to say what I really felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:22.52,Main,,0,0,0,,You were the first, Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:25.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:30.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:31.86,Main,,0,0,0,,...Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.59,0:00:56.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The truth rests solely on{\i0}\N{\i1}the front/back of a card{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:01:01.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has not yet been solved{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.94,0:01:11.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Upon the dazzling, dizzying stage,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:23.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}destroy those entangled emotions{\i0}\N{\i1}as many times as it takes to satisfy you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should the tomorrows{\i0}\N{\i1}wandering after fate's beckoning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:33.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}choose and discard so that{\i0}\N{\i1}they can become one?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.89,0:01:39.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't afford to disclose my reproachable hand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:44.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The days spent draining{\i0}\N{\i1}the already-dry sea of regret{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:49.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}desire within limited words forgiveness{\i0}\N{\i1}for the unplanned smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.86,0:01:54.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't mind forgetting reality{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:59.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to know anything now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.87,0:02:01.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:14.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you're going to be late for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:16.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:18.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma will clean up the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:20.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:45.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Morning, Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:47.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:50.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it time to go to school already?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:52.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, you're such a sleepy-head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:17.99,Main,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:26.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:28.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you alone today?\NWhere's Yuzuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:31.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, um, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:47.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Is Akira still missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:51.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. A girl from her school said so.\NShe hasn't come home at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:54.19,Main,,0,0,0,,It's been about a week, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:04.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru, the train's going to go. Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:25.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:29.94,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right... We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:33.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's... not be friends anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:36.82,Main,,0,0,0,,We're... not friends anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:39.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't battle anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:43.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki won't quit battling\Nuntil her wish comes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:46.41,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what we decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:51.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes... decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:04:59.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:00.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Kurebayashi, in the second-year class...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:02.01,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean the twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:04.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard they're going out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:05.51,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:07.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't that ince--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.02,Main,,0,0,0,,No way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:12.35,Main,,0,0,0,,So, the rumor was true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:14.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they "did it" already...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:16.77,Main,,0,0,0,,--What'd you think? They live together.\N--No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:18.69,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault, Honoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:20.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Really, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:22.65,Main,,0,0,0,,And I thought he was cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Gross...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:32.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you spread it to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:33.96,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "spread"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:37.09,Main,,0,0,0,,It's your fault for doing stuff that would spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.09,0:05:40.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I just said that you were acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:43.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I just discussed it with the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:45.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Honoka was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:50.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I felt sorry that you and Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}\Nwere being misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:55.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. But, I can't forgive\Nanyone who insults Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:58.48,Main,,0,0,0,,C-Can't forgive...?! That's so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:00.11,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:03.11,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why everyone is saying\Nyou're both making out and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:04.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.70,Main,,0,0,0,,What a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:07.49,Main,,0,0,0,,It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:09.83,Main,,0,0,0,,--Aren't they like, brother and sister...?\N--That's why it's freaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:12.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Too bad. I thought she was cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:26.26,Main,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:30.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:34.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard you told the others not to insult me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:35.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:41.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy. But you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:43.78,Main,,0,0,0,,After all, it is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:46.49,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "true"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:49.78,Main,,0,0,0,,...love you, Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:51.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:55.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I've loved you... ever since we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:07:01.34,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I thought saying that\Nwould make you feel sick about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:04.51,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought... for the longest time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:07.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess Goto-{\i1}kun {\i0}in the second class...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:09.18,Main,,0,0,0,,That sounds okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:10.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:11.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:16.48,Main,,0,0,0,,As I got older, all the kids\Naround me had others they liked...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, how about you Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:19.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:21.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone said who they liked,\Nso it's your turn next!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Who do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:27.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I'm not into boys now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:29.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, quit lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:33.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Really. There's no one that I like at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.33,Main,,0,0,0,,You're still lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:35.79,Main,,0,0,0,,No, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:36.96,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon, tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:39.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:41.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell the truth to anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:48.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, do you know if...\NKazuki-{\i1}kun {\i0}has a person he likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:53.01,Main,,0,0,0,,H-He was saying that he thought\Nthings like that were creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:58.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Even when he watches TV, he said those\Nlove stories were boring and unreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:01.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I lied to my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:05.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Even to the person I love... Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:10.45,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I was thinking maybe it's best like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:17.00,Main,,0,0,0,,What? You're fine like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:18.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:22.21,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I'll still love Kazuki forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:27.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if he gets a girlfriend,\Nand marries, and has kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:30.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll continue to lie my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:36.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Even when I'm old and single,\NI'll love him forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:41.02,Main,,0,0,0,,But... that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:45.86,Main,,0,0,0,,A card game?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:47.86,Main,,0,0,0,,It's pretty fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:54.49,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:55.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:01.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you the Selector?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:02.50,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:05.75,Main,,0,0,0,,My name is Hanayo. Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:08.72,Main,,0,0,0,,The card... talked?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:10.72,Main,,0,0,0,,The card did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:14.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't you hear her, Kazuki? This card just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:16.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:19.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Our voices can only be heard by Selectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:22.23,Main,,0,0,0,,S-Selector...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:26.11,Main,,0,0,0,,My wish... can come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:30.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Right. Whether you\Nbelieve that or not is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.49,Main,,0,0,0,,You have a wish, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:40.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Not like you'll lose anything.\NGo ahead, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:45.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I... love Ka--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.50,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:49.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I... love Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:53.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki? You mean... your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:03.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I... love Kazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:05.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I... love Kazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:07.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:12.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I love Kazuki! Love... Love...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:13.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I love him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:17.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I know... This isn't right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.54,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't forgiven!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:24.12,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I want to be with him.\NI want to be with Kazuki forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:27.59,Main,,0,0,0,,No... I want to be Kazuki's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:30.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to be his girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:36.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:38.47,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll make that wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:46.48,Main,,0,0,0,,So, your wish is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:50.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I was really doing my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:53.11,Main,,0,0,0,,...being straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Straightforward in what I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:57.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Straightforwardly hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:10:59.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Straightforwardly hurt others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:04.21,Main,,0,0,0,,It was the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:05.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:10.17,Main,,0,0,0,,...I was able to say what I really felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:12.71,Main,,0,0,0,,You were the first, Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:16.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:19.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks... Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:26.10,Main,,0,0,0,,If I could be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:28.52,Main,,0,0,0,,no matter how hurt I was,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.90,Main,,0,0,0,,no matter if the entire\Nworld were against me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:33.74,Main,,0,0,0,,or even if I lost everything,\Nit wouldn't have mattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:37.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I love you, Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:01.72,Main,,0,0,0,,He hasn't come back from lunch yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:02.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:04.52,Main,,0,0,0,,She's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:07.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Pretty creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:18.61,Main,,0,0,0,,A wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:22.83,Main,,0,0,0,,A wish you want to make come true,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:28.29,Main,,0,0,0,,even if it means hurting yourself,\Neven if it means hurting someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:32.00,Main,,0,0,0,,The next time we meet, I'll be a new me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:34.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Me, as Kazuki's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:40.84,Main,,0,0,0,,That kind of straightforward\Nfeeling can't be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:59.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I... don't have a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:00.61,Main,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:03.66,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what we are about...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:06.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Me... and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.75,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:11.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:13.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru? Lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:20.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:24.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Because Hitoe and Yuzuki\Naren't friends anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:27.89,Main,,0,0,0,,But, Tama is Ru's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:30.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:35.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if we don't battle... Always friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:37.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:39.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I like to battle, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:42.78,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I can... stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:46.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks... Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:48.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:52.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:57.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:01.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe? Why are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:04.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait. Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:06.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:08.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe has an LRIG!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:12.73,Main,,0,0,0,,LRIG?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:16.44,Main,,0,0,0,,You're... a Selector, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:18.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Please battle me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:20.36,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:25.28,Main,,0,0,0,,It can't be... You're a Selector again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:29.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Please... battle me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:31.83,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:34.33,Main,,0,0,0,,No... Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:40.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I'm not battling anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:44.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Right, and you're still\Nhanging around with Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:46.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:50.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess that can't be helped.\NYou're both really close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:56.86,Main,,0,0,0,,But if so, why not listen to\Na favor from your former friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:15:00.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Where...? Where are you, Yuzuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:12.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:17.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Long time no see... Well, not really, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:21.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki... an LRIG?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:24.47,Main,,0,0,0,,This can't be real... This...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:25.88,Main,,0,0,0,,This can't be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:29.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's actually pretty real.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:33.22,Main,,0,0,0,,That scrunchie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:35.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like the three of us got together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:39.31,Main,,0,0,0,,But, this feels so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:40.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:42.07,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:45.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Really, there's a lot to talk about,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:47.32,Main,,0,0,0,,but before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:50.66,Main,,0,0,0,,...battle Hitoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:53.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't! I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:55.16,Main,,0,0,0,,It's for Hitoe's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:16:00.34,Main,,0,0,0,,For Hitoe's wish... For me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:02.25,Main,,0,0,0,,My wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:05.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:08.63,Main,,0,0,0,,For Hitoe and Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:26.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:30.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:32.16,Main,,0,0,0,,--Open!\N--Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:50.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe... Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:16:58.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama! Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:16:59.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:04.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Yuzuki! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:12.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I won my battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:16.54,Main,,0,0,0,,And... my wish was approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:22.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Your final attack... your final call. Together...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:33.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, together with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:36.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I accept...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:38.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I... accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:40.81,Main,,0,0,0,,...the laws of the Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:43.02,Main,,0,0,0,,...the laws of the Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:44.02,Main,,0,0,0,,And...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:47.98,Main,,0,0,0,,--...now, a new Eternal Girl will be born!\N--...now, a new Eternal Girl will be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.61,Main,,0,0,0,,--Adamasphere!\N--Adamasphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:18.01,Main,,0,0,0,,What...? Then, the Yuzuki now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:24.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:27.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:29.28,Main,,0,0,0,,...became Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:31.82,Main,,0,0,0,,The girl whose wish was approved
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:34.11,Main,,0,0,0,,becomes an Eternal Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:37.53,Main,,0,0,0,,and gains the power\Nto make wishes come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:39.62,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.58,Main,,0,0,0,,...the wish is granted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:05.02,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the drawing I made during pre-school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:07.44,Main,,0,0,0,,The princess is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:09.69,Main,,0,0,0,,The black scribble next to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:11.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know who that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:13.65,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:17.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I drew you as the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:20.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be your bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:24.16,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I learned that was a bad thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:27.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I tried to make it go away,\Nover and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:31.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I colored over it so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:35.67,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I couldn't make it go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:39.60,Main,,0,0,0,,"Go away"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:43.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I couldn't make\Nmy feelings go away, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:52.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I love you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:56.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I love you too, Yuzuki... I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:59.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I've loved you for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:03.41,Main,,0,0,0,,We were family. That wouldn't be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:05.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I deceived myself all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:09.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I tried to not notice my feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:13.51,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I don't care what happens anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:15.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care what others think!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:20.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't mind losing everything\Nand leaving this place together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:24.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I love you, Yuzuki! I love you! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:32.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I... love you too, Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:36.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:38.15,Main,,0,0,0,,The wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:40.07,Main,,0,0,0,,...came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:44.99,Main,,0,0,0,,That... That can't be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:48.29,Main,,0,0,0,,The LRIG... gets the wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:54.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:58.47,Main,,0,0,0,,...will become an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:18.65,Main,,0,0,0,,The replaced Selector...\Nbecomes another person's LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:30.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.21,0:21:35.75,Main,,0,0,0,,And when that person is led\Nto victory, and is replaced...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:39.05,Main,,0,0,0,,...the LRIG can come back\Nout in the world again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.72,0:21:45.01,Main,,0,0,0,,The wish will come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:47.93,Main,,0,0,0,,But the wish comes true,\Nnot for me, the Selector...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:49.93,Main,,0,0,0,,...but instead for Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}, the LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:52.52,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the Eternal Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:54.44,Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:56.78,Main,,0,0,0,,...the truth behind these battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:14.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nodding to the clockwork shadow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:19.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}opens the door to the end,{\i0}\N{\i1}bringing in the darkness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:25.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There we catch glimpses of the perilous answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.64,0:22:31.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today's prayer becomes taboo tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:37.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The upside-down maze reflects{\i0}\N{\i1}the heavens and the earth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:43.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The gear begins to turn{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.15,0:22:49.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen carefully among the masses{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:59.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and that bell resounding in{\i0}\N{\i1}the skies beckons the soul...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:06.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must move forward even beyond eternity{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:12.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because it is the future I chose{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The unreachable summer clouds{\i0}\N{\i1}and flickering heat haze{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:25.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day I'll get back my place of smiles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.54,0:23:33.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:35.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.37,0:23:36.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:40.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}... you're so horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.21,0:23:41.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.30,0:23:44.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks... Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.72,0:23:47.05,Main,,0,0,0,,"That Stranded Emotion."
